race.description: The Lids Fly On Ladbrokes Live Channels
race.comment: NITROUS OCTANE (5) has a strong record this track and trip with two wins and two placings from six starts. In the money last time at this track (20.16) in a Grade 5, finishing a 5.5 lengths second. Appeals as a leading chance in this. SPRING GOOLAGONG (4) finished in the placings last time but could not have been more impressive before that in her outstanding 19.71 win at this track over 350m. Has the ability and can find winning form again. SPRING GOLD (1) boasts a strong record this journey here with seven wins and three minors from 20 tries. Below best last time at this track (21.14) in a Grade 5, finishing a 19 length eighth. Can feature with the right run. DIG DEEP RUPEE (2) must be included in calculations.
